      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait i'm confused. what do you mean by \"goblins prefer things a bit hotter\"? i thought we were just talking about the chemical reaction in the dough. can you just stick to the science and explain the actual difference between the Maillard reaction and caramelization? like, how does the chemistry change between the two?",
